"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯！<br />\n台灣其實都想減少對中國嘅依賴<br />\n<br />\n另外，依家其實好多廠都搬咗去越南，係咪其實都可以拉攏埋越南？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申唔識經濟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:59:46.000Z","msg":"越南比香港同台灣更仇共"},{"pid":"42ac4c59cbd33e36243a95f885d0eca1d9e95598","tid":1827118,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9084a62edf365b84b3dcaad3e288a0ff70c5c63","tid":1827118,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T17:01:01.000Z","msg":"我要食台灣生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}